But yeah, K.J. man, The only man I would ever want to just hang with, who is also a celebrity, And I have had chance to chill with Johnny Depp, Chris Evans, a few others, My cousin is an actress who is under the wing of the man who played the bad guy in Big Trouble in Little China, he's an awesome cat too. But Kevin, would just be cool to sit around with and soak up all his knowledge that he would hopefully bestow upon me. Just about life in general. You know a man who has a black belt has some things about life to teach people. Awesome Day
